extendedInfo.description: The American Association of Oral and Maxillofacial Surgeons (AAOMS) is the professional organization representing more than 9,000 oral and maxillofacial surgeons. The AAOMS 2012 Dental Implant Conference will be held in Chicago, Illinois, at the Sheraton Chicago Hotel & Towers, November 29 - December 1, 2012.
